        <updateDate>2019-08-16T22:23:12Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Crime Gun Tracing Modernization Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the National Tracing Center within the Bureau of Alcohol, Tobacco, Firearms and Explosives to establish and maintain an electronic, searchable database of records related to firearms transactions. <br /></p>]]></text>
